{"type":"message_update","assistantMessageEvent":{"type":"toolcall_start","contentIndex":1,"partial":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is giving me instructions to act as a council member for an AAR (Automated Arbitration Resolution) case. Let me break down what I need to do:\n\n1. Use the Pi MCP proxy tool named `mcp` to call AAR tools\n2. The tools are prefixed with `aar_` \n3. First, I need to call `mcp` with `{\"tool\":\"aar_wait_for_opportunity\",\"args\":\"{}\"}`\n4. If it returns `state: waiting`, I need to call it again with the returned `after_version`\n5. If it returns `state: ready`, I need to read the returned information (prompt, turn, limits, remaining time, attempts remaining, opportunity id)\n6. Review the visible arbitration record and admitted evidence using appropriate tools\n7. When ready, submit my vote using `aar_submit_council_vote`\n8. Stop after receiving `ok: true`\n\nLet me start by calling the wait_for_opportunity tool.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.mcp:0","name":"mcp","arguments":{},"partialArgs":"","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782787891239,"responseId":"gen-1782787891-jXDUEIVHypYOQRSqsZaN","responseModel":"moonshotai/kimi-k2-thinking-20251106"}},"message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is giving me instructions to act as a council member for an AAR (Automated Arbitration Resolution) case. Let me break down what I need to do:\n\n1. Use the Pi MCP proxy tool named `mcp` to call AAR tools\n2. The tools are prefixed with `aar_` \n3. First, I need to call `mcp` with `{\"tool\":\"aar_wait_for_opportunity\",\"args\":\"{}\"}`\n4. If it returns `state: waiting`, I need to call it again with the returned `after_version`\n5. If it returns `state: ready`, I need to read the returned information (prompt, turn, limits, remaining time, attempts remaining, opportunity id)\n6. Review the visible arbitration record and admitted evidence using appropriate tools\n7. When ready, submit my vote using `aar_submit_council_vote`\n8. Stop after receiving `ok: true`\n\nLet me start by calling the wait_for_opportunity tool.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.mcp:0","name":"mcp","arguments":{},"partialArgs":"","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782787891239,"responseId":"gen-1782787891-jXDUEIVHypYOQRSqsZaN","responseModel":"moonshotai/kimi-k2-thinking-20251106"}}
