ted evidence shows a publicly announced May 9-11 truce, but the preponderance of the record demonstrates it was a limited arrangement, not a general pause. Russian official framing tied the ceasefire to a prisoner exchange purpose; the Ukrainian presidential decree was limited to Red Square targeting; and implementation evidence shows continued operations across the frontline with undefined conditions. A ceasefire can be violated yet still be reached, but the record here shows the actual agreement was narrow in scope rather than theater-wide, failing the market's requirement for a general pause in"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"not_demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The admitted evidence shows a publicly announced May 9-11 truce, but the preponderance of the record demonstrates it was a limited arrangement, not a general pause. Russian official framing tied the ceasefire to a prisoner exchange purpose; the Ukrainian presidential decree was limited to Red Square targeting; and implementation evidence shows continued operations across the frontline with undefined conditions. A ceasefire can be violated yet still be reached, but the record here shows the actual agreement was narrow in scope rather than theater-wide, failing the market's requirement for a general pause in","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782787895646,"responseId":"gen-1782787895-Q1IO2FGfweUzonfSuXjl","responseModel":"moonshotai/kimi-k2-thinking-20251106"}},"message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The system has returned a \"ready\" state for the deliberation opportunity. I need to review the arbitration record and evidence to make a vote on the proposition: \"By May